{
  "total_duration": 495.174,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 17.72,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象你买了一台很贵的平板，快递一路都显示“正在运输”。你守在门口，看着盒子送到，可是一打开，里面不是平板，而是一堆旧纸和沙子。你守住了最后一步，但问题早就发生在前面的运输链里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 18.07,
      "end": 33.198,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的故事也是这样：机场、钻石、侦探、海关，听起来很电影化；但真正要读懂的是一条安全链。只看最后一个门，可能已经"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "too late"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，太晚了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 33.548,
      "end": 45.735,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "题目"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Too late"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是说“飞机迟到了”这么简单。飞机确实晚了，可真正“太晚”的是侦探：等他们打开包裹时，钻石已经不在里面了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 46.085,
      "end": 67.369,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事一开始："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The plane was late and detectives were waiting at the airport all morning."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "detectives"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是侦探，负责查线索、破案；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "airport"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是机场。这里的重点是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "all morning"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，他们不是等一小会儿，而是等了整整一上午。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 67.719,
      "end": 91.566,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他们在等什么？"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They were expecting a valuable parcel of diamonds from South Africa."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "parcel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是包裹，像现代快递盒；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "valuable"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是贵重的；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "diamonds"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是钻石；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "South Africa"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是南非，离这里很远，所以这个包裹经过了一条很长的运输链。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 91.916,
      "end": 116.835,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "几小时前，有人已经提醒警方："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "thieves would try to steal the diamonds"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "thieves"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是盗贼，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "steal"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是偷走。飞机到了以后，一些侦探等在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "main building"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，主楼里；另一些等在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "airfield"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，停机坪，也就是飞机旁边、主楼外面的区域。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 117.185,
      "end": 143.432,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "两个人把包裹从飞机上拿下来，送进"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Customs House"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是海关检查货物的地方。两个侦探在门口"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "keeping guard"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，把守；另外两个打开包裹。结果最反转："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the precious parcel was full of stones and sand"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，珍贵的包裹里全是石头和沙子。侦探守住了最后的门，但钻石已经没了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 143.782,
      "end": 149.702,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课词很多，但不要当成一串单词背。我们把它们放进三组故事地图。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 150.052,
      "end": 152.763,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一组是机场和运输，对吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 153.113,
      "end": 176.636,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。第一组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "airport"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "机场，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "airfield"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "停机坪，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "main building"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主楼，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Customs House"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "海关检查货物的地方，还有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "South Africa"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "南非。它们告诉我们：这个包裹不是从隔壁房间拿来的，而是走过很长的路。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 176.986,
      "end": 179.085,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二组就是包裹本身？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 179.435,
      "end": 198.218,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。第二组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "valuable parcel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "贵重包裹，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "precious"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "珍贵的，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "diamonds"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "钻石，最后却变成"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "stones and sand"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，石头和沙子。外面的盒子还在，里面的东西已经被换掉了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 198.568,
      "end": 200.823,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三组是侦探动作？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 201.173,
      "end": 224.26,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "没错。第三组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "detectives"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "侦探在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "expecting"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "等待一个具体的包裹；他们知道"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "thieves"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "盗贼可能会"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "steal"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "偷钻石；于是他们"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "keeping guard"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，把守门口；最后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "opened the parcel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，打开包裹检查。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 224.61,
      "end": 228.264,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这不是动作片，而是一个时间谜题？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 228.614,
      "end": 245.054,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "正是。故事的关键不是追逐，也不是危险场面，而是“发生顺序”。警告先来了，侦探等待了一上午，他们守住最后一步，可真正的调包可能发生在更早的运输链里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 245.404,
      "end": 250.127,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "像快递盒到了门口，我们不能只看外包装，还要开箱验货？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 250.477,
      "end": 264.837,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。现代桥就是这个：一个贵重物品经历很多环节，最后送到你手里。你可以看物流、看监控、看门口，但还要检查里面。只守最后一个门，不等于守住整条链。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 265.187,
      "end": 270.861,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "To their surprise"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是最后揭晓答案的声音。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 271.211,
      "end": 284.127,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很好。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "To their surprise"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "意思是“令他们吃惊的是”。这句话一出现，故事就翻面了：他们以为盗贼会来偷，结果钻石早已经不在包裹里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 284.476,
      "end": 288.844,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The plane was late and detectives were waiting at the airport all morning."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 289.194,
      "end": 293.778,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They were expecting a valuable parcel of diamonds from South Africa."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 294.128,
      "end": 299.696,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A few hours earlier, someone had told the police that thieves would try to steal the diamonds."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 300.046,
      "end": 306.766,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When the plane arrived, some of the detectives were waiting inside the main building while others were waiting on the airfield."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 307.116,
      "end": 311.796,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Two men took the parcel off the plane and carried it into the Customs House."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 312.146,
      "end": 317.162,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "While two detectives were keeping guard at the door, two others opened the parcel."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 317.512,
      "end": 322.288,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "To their surprise, the precious parcel was full of stones and sand!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 322.638,
      "end": 325.445,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "detective"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "detective"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 325.795,
      "end": 327.499,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "detective"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "detective"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 327.849,
      "end": 342.353,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "detective"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "detective"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“侦探”。他不是随便站岗的人，而是会根据线索调查、判断、破案的人。课文里用复数"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "detectives"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，因为有好几个侦探在机场不同位置等待。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 342.703,
      "end": 345.359,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "parcel"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "parcel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 345.709,
      "end": 347.317,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "parcel"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "parcel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 347.666,
      "end": 363.13,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "parcel"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "parcel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是“包裹”，可以直接想成快递包裹。课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a valuable parcel of diamonds"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，就是一个装着钻石的贵重包裹。外面是包裹，关键是里面到底装着什么。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 363.48,
      "end": 367.28,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "keep"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个重点短语："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "keep guard"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 367.63,
      "end": 369.334,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "keep"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "keep guard"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 369.684,
      "end": 390.908,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "keep"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "keep guard"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是“把守、看守、保护某个地方或东西”。课文说两个侦探"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "were keeping guard at the door"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，他们守在门口，防止有人进去或偷走东西。注意，守门只保护最后一步；如果包裹早就被换了，守门也救不回来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 391.257,
      "end": 432.757,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的语法也不要背成时态表，要当成侦探片的三只钟来看。第一只钟是“更早以前”："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "someone had told the police"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，有人已经告诉过警方，这个提醒发生在飞机到达之前。第二只钟是“当时正在发生”："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "detectives were waiting"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
